睇劇情，啲npc 行幾步就撞牆<br />\n<br />\n但整體黎講，隻game都算好玩。可以等佢出哂三部曲再玩都未遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:24:12.000Z","msg":"第二第三部曲據聞好似會當新game出"},{"pid":"b28b35de3236cb02fd4d9d3f36f5e6ff226f3083","tid":611634,"uid":69134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4f448c996396dd2922739599bea2c52c02ee61d","tid":611634,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:17:40.000Z","msg":"太多bug<br />\n玩玩下又crash<br />\n垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:36:11.000Z","msg":"無可否認Bugs係多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係crash自己玩落好似又唔係好見<br />\n但因此評呢隻game為垃圾又太武斷<br />\n建議可以稍等一下，過半年等佢fix d bugs fix得7788再番黎（岩岩呢幾日又出左patch又fix左堆bugs，可見制作團隊都有心既），可能係另一番新天地，如果都係唔岩玩就放棄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，始終隻game題材模式都比較小眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be68d4e72c93c568200851fea7726305513cef78","tid":611634,"uid":23549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:43:30.000Z","msg":"執番啲bugs先買"},{"pid":"327e72cfdd1fbe84a87cb7feb96f981781432484","tid":611634,"uid":17353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:43:50.000Z","msg":"故事正，bug多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}